id=torchbutton
name=Torch Button
version=v1.1.2
versionCode=4
author=nogrep
description=Long-press Power toggles the flashlight when the screen is off or locked. Long-press shows the system power dialog when the screen is on and unlocked. Long-press always turns the flashlight off if it is on. Power+Vol chords (screenshot, assistant) keep working. Can be enabled/disabled from the bundled "Torch Button" app and a Quick Settings tile.
